data.description: Cute starter home or investment property that features 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath. Spacious living room as you walk in the front door. Dining room is located in between the kitchen and living room. Refrigerator will stay. Fenced in back yard with a storage shed and covered patio. Close to major highways and shopping centers.
